

This is a project in which you can register yourself for events.
1)When you open the index.html file,on the very first page, you will so some listed events, when you scroll down you will see information about those events.
2)When you see the register button and press it, you will reach three options and when you select the event you want to get registered in, You register yourself by pressing the register button and then after that you are supposed to log in
3)After you log in, you will see an alert box giving the message of your successful registration.
4)After that your email address will be registered for the event on the database(you can ask me for the screenshot of the registered email address:))
